30004693@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1207@LMC@2019-06-14
30004694@@@@@@Nanyang Technological University (NTU) is a 200-hectare campus well-equipped with academics facilities.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1208@LMC@2019-06-14
30004695@@@@@@There are more than 30 lecture theatres and over a hundred tutorial rooms in the many buildings within NTU.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1209@LMC@2019-06-14
30004696@@@@@@However, with such a large campus, students in NTU, especially freshmen, may find it challenging to find their exact venue for different classes.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1210@LMC@2019-06-14
30004697@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1211@LMC@2019-06-14
30004698@@@@@@With the difficulty in locating the exact lecture theatres and tutorial rooms to attend classes, students waste precious time wandering around the different buildings, and as a result, some are even late for classes, which can be disruptive to the lessons being conducted.@@@@1@43@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1212@LMC@2019-06-14
30004699@@@@@@The current directory in the campus is not very interactive.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1213@LMC@2019-06-14
30004700@@@@@@Even though the online platform on NTU’s website, maps.ntu.edu.sg, states specific routes to different location, it may still be insufficient to a freshmen that is unaware of their exact location.@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1214@LMC@2019-06-14
30004701@@@@@@Therefore, there is a need to improve the means to address this problem.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1215@LMC@2019-06-14
30004702@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1216@LMC@2019-06-14
30004703@@@@@@With such a technologically-savvy generation, a mobile application software named ‘Find your NTU!’ can be developed for students to find their way around in NTU campus.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1217@LMC@2019-06-14
30004704@@@@@@‘Find your NTU!’ will make use of the mobile phone’s Global Positioning System(GPS) to pinpoint their exact location in the NTU campus, and guide them to the exact venues of their lessons.@@@@1@32@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1218@LMC@2019-06-14
30004705@@@@@@‘Find your NTU!’ will be specifically catered to the map of NTU campus, and will recognize the terms used to name the tutorial rooms and lecture theatres, for instances, TR +50 or LT19A.@@@@1@33@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1219@LMC@2019-06-14
30004706@@@@@@‘Find your NTU!’ will be designed to be user-friendly, free to use, and require minimal data usage.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1220@LMC@2019-06-14
30004707@@@@@@Moreover, it will be made compatible with the different operating systems of the various brands of mobile devices, such as iOS for iPhones, Android for Samsung phones, to make it accessible for everyone.@@@@1@33@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1221@LMC@2019-06-14
30004708@@@@@@In addition, it will be updated monthly to include new sections of the school campus, or include areas that newly under renovation, so that users will be accurately guided to their intended locations.@@@@1@33@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1222@LMC@2019-06-14
30004709@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1223@LMC@2019-06-14
30004710@@@@@@With ‘Find your NTU!’, it can be much more convenient to navigate in NTU.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1224@LMC@2019-06-14
30004711@@@@@@This can lead to massive time savings to each individual student, as one gets from one venue to another for different modules more effectively and efficiently.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1225@LMC@2019-06-14
30004712@@@@@@This can eventually benefit NTU population as classes start and end on schedule.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1226@LMC@2019-06-14
30004713@@@@@@Furthermore, it can be easily implemented with smartphones commonly owned by students in NTU.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1227@LMC@2019-06-14
30004714@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1228@LMC@2019-06-14
30004715@@@@@@‘Find your NTU!’ can be made known to students through the NTU school email during the first week of each semester, and after which, simply download ‘Find your NTU!’ on their mobile devices and one can utilize the application and start navigating his way around the NTU campus easily.@@@@1@49@ntucle-docid:161; ntucle-sid:1229@LMC@2019-06-14
