30004722@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1286@LMC@2019-06-14
30004723@@@@@@Transportation system has been one of the most beneficial and oldest innovations in human civilization.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1287@LMC@2019-06-14
30004724@@@@@@Human always seek after for an effective transportation system, no matter it is by means of conveniences or, to increase productivity.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1288@LMC@2019-06-14
30004725@@@@@@Safety is often the main issue regarding transportation, thus most transportation systems are well equipped with various forms of safety precautious measures, such as the air bags, safety belts and Antilock-Braking System.@@@@1@32@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1289@LMC@2019-06-14
30004726@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1290@LMC@2019-06-14
30004727@@@@@@However, it always seems that we have overlooked something in this field of innovation – bicycles.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1291@LMC@2019-06-14
30004728@@@@@@According to an article published by ASIAONE NEWS on 18thJuly2012, despite the decrease in overall road accident cases, fatalities involving cyclists are still rising.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1292@LMC@2019-06-14
30004729@@@@@@Bikes are no doubt one of the most dangerous forms of transportation, yet its safety measures has done minimal improvement throughout these decades.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1293@LMC@2019-06-14
30004730@@@@@@Often cyclists would wear a safety helmet to serve as a protection, but its ability to prevent major injuries is still an uncertainty.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1294@LMC@2019-06-14
30004731@@@@@@Therefore, an upgrade for the helmets is utmost needed.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1295@LMC@2019-06-14
30004732@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1296@LMC@2019-06-14
30004733@@@@@@I would like to introduce the Indicator Helm as an effective measure to solve the increasing road accident issues.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1297@LMC@2019-06-14
30004734@@@@@@Indicator Helm is a helmet that has a LED light board attached at the back of the helmet to inform the other road users the direction that the cyclist wish to turn by showing right or left arrow.@@@@1@38@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1298@LMC@2019-06-14
30004735@@@@@@It is relatively simple to turn on the indicator, for right direction, user simply has to press the button which to be clipped on the right handle of the bicycle; there will be a left button as well for left direction.@@@@1@41@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1299@LMC@2019-06-14
30004736@@@@@@Signals from the button pressed are sent to the LED board via Bluetooth Connection.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1300@LMC@2019-06-14
30004737@@@@@@Furthermore, the helmet also has reflective stickers to allow cyclist to be noticeable even in the darkest night.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1301@LMC@2019-06-14
30004738@@@@@@Moreover, the helmet has built-in motion-sensor-gyroscopes, allowing the LED light board to be lit up in red whenever the cyclist decelerates.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1302@LMC@2019-06-14
30004739@@@@@@Benefit@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1303@LMC@2019-06-14
30004740@@@@@@First of all, the indicators shown are clear and will not cause confusion to others.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1304@LMC@2019-06-14
30004741@@@@@@In addition, LED light bulb is the best option because it is proven to be energy efficient and it shines an optimum amount of light to be noticeable without causing distractions for other road users.@@@@1@35@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1305@LMC@2019-06-14
30004742@@@@@@The LED board is waterproof, thus it will still be functioning well even if it is raining.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1306@LMC@2019-06-14
30004743@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:162; ntucle-sid:1307@LMC@2019-06-14
