30004762@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1203@LMC@2019-06-14
30004763@@@@@@Cake is one of the most amazing things ever.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1204@LMC@2019-06-14
30004764@@@@@@It is known to be a form of dessert.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1205@LMC@2019-06-14
30004765@@@@@@Many of us have it during celebratory occasions.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1206@LMC@2019-06-14
