30004768@@@@@@2@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1209@LMC@2019-06-14
30004769@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1210@LMC@2019-06-14
30004770@@@@@@Not only to us, but also to the staffs of many cake shops, it is difficult to cut a circular cake to the number of pieces you want evenly or to the size you want it to be.@@@@1@38@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1211@LMC@2019-06-14
30004771@@@@@@Many times, all of us will get slices of different sizes.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1212@LMC@2019-06-14
30004772@@@@@@Some will get the smaller slice one, while others may get more than what they can eat.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1213@LMC@2019-06-14
30004773@@@@@@This causes disappointments, or worst, wastage of food.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1214@LMC@2019-06-14
30004774@@@@@@For shops that usually sell cakes in slices, it is unfair for some customers to get a bigger slice than others when both are paying the same amount.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1215@LMC@2019-06-14
30004775@@@@@@Therefore, a tool is needed to solve it.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1216@LMC@2019-06-14
30004776@@@@@@3@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1217@LMC@2019-06-14
30004777@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1218@LMC@2019-06-14
30004778@@@@@@The “Cake Chart”, a cake cutter, is invented.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1219@LMC@2019-06-14
30004779@@@@@@This cake cutter looks just like a circular metal container with a base of 14 inch.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1220@LMC@2019-06-14
30004780@@@@@@The sides can be detached from the base and have slits on its inner sides.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1221@LMC@2019-06-14
30004781@@@@@@There will be metal pieces, where two long pieces are meant to be place in the middle as shown in the diagram below (Fig1).@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1222@LMC@2019-06-14
30004782@@@@@@The metal pieces are knifes with good scallops, each with little curve coming to a point and it is thin and flexible.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1223@LMC@2019-06-14
30004783@@@@@@Users can slide the smaller metal pieces into the slits according to the way they want the cake to be cut after the two long pieces is being placed.@@@@1@29@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1224@LMC@2019-06-14
30004784@@@@@@To use this tool, base need to be detached.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1225@LMC@2019-06-14
30004785@@@@@@Place the cake below those metal pieces and press those metal pieces down the centre of the cake.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1226@LMC@2019-06-14
30004786@@@@@@Fig1 Top view of "Cake Chart"@@@@1@6@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1227@LMC@2019-06-14
30004787@@@@@@4@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1228@LMC@2019-06-14
30004788@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1229@LMC@2019-06-14
30004789@@@@@@It allows convenience as you can cut the number of cake you want all at once, and everybody get the same size of cake.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1230@LMC@2019-06-14
30004790@@@@@@Size of the slice can also be adjusted according to request, if anyone wants a bigger slice, by changing how you place the metal pieces.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1231@LMC@2019-06-14
30004791@@@@@@And for cake shops, customers can be ensured that they will get the same size of cake as everyone else that purchases it.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:164; ntucle-sid:1232@LMC@2019-06-14
