30005067@@@@@@Due to the lack of clean water, it becomes common for the locals of the area be more susceptible to illnesses such as vomiting and diarrhea which may exacerbate dehydration (WHO, 2013).@@@@1@32@ntucle-docid:181; ntucle-sid:1547@LMC@2019-06-14
