30005154@@@@@@[3][4] This is especially common for the middle-aged working group.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:183; ntucle-sid:1597@LMC@2019-06-14
30005155@@@@@@[5]@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:183; ntucle-sid:1598@LMC@2019-06-14
