30005440@@@@@@Flash flood has always been a major problem in Singapore.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1423@LMC@2019-06-14
30005441@@@@@@According to Public Utilities Board (PUB), Singapore’s National Water Agency, the annual rainfall is 2,344.0 mm (92.28 inches).@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1424@LMC@2019-06-14
30005442@@@@@@Given the high intensity of the rain, with limited infrastructure, flash flood can occur around 10-12 days annually.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1425@LMC@2019-06-14
30005443@@@@@@This causes economic losses and affects social activities.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1426@LMC@2019-06-14
30005444@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1427@LMC@2019-06-14
30005445@@@@@@To avoid water pounding in constructions, there are two ways existing in the market.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1428@LMC@2019-06-14
30005446@@@@@@One is to use a diesel pump to increase the drainage capacity during a heavy rain.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1429@LMC@2019-06-14
30005447@@@@@@Another is to create extra barriers to alleviate water penetration.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1430@LMC@2019-06-14
30005448@@@@@@However, they have obvious limitations.@@@@1@5@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1431@LMC@2019-06-14
30005449@@@@@@The diesel pump is run by contractors.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1432@LMC@2019-06-14
30005450@@@@@@Time is required for them to deploy the pump to the ponding site.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1433@LMC@2019-06-14
30005451@@@@@@Furthermore, when there is a pervasive intensive rain, only few buildings can be served.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1434@LMC@2019-06-14
30005452@@@@@@The extra barrier can only deter water penetration at designed level.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1435@LMC@2019-06-14
30005453@@@@@@Once the rainfall exceeds the limit, the building will be flooded.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1436@LMC@2019-06-14
30005454@@@@@@Therefore, a system can be adapted in house widely and constantly flush out ponding water is needed.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1437@LMC@2019-06-14
30005455@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1438@LMC@2019-06-14
30005456@@@@@@The objective of this proposal is to integrate a siphon system called Flood Flusher into the buildings.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1439@LMC@2019-06-14
30005457@@@@@@The basic shape of the system is a U-shape pipe, with one end in the building and another connected to the underground drainage canal.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1440@LMC@2019-06-14
30005458@@@@@@The interior part is a long flexible tube with a mouth that has several shapes to be chosen.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1441@LMC@2019-06-14
30005459@@@@@@The outer part is a fixed PVC pipe.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1442@LMC@2019-06-14
30005460@@@@@@The pipe at the roof and has a rain collection funnel.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1443@LMC@2019-06-14
30005461@@@@@@Initially, the whole system is closed at both ends of the siphon.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1444@LMC@2019-06-14
30005462@@@@@@During a heavy rain, the system will be filled with water quickly.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1445@LMC@2019-06-14
30005463@@@@@@Once any ponding or water leakage is observed, user can close the rain collection funnel and open both ends of the siphon.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1446@LMC@2019-06-14
30005464@@@@@@The interior tube mouth will provide a sucking force due to height difference.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1447@LMC@2019-06-14
30005465@@@@@@User can choose desired shape of mouth to remove water.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1448@LMC@2019-06-14
30005466@@@@@@The water will be discharged to the drainage canal.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1449@LMC@2019-06-14
30005467@@@@@@This system can constantly clear water as long as the rain continues to refill the siphon.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1450@LMC@2019-06-14
30005468@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1451@LMC@2019-06-14
30005469@@@@@@This system is much lower energy consuming and can be activated immediately.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1452@LMC@2019-06-14
30005470@@@@@@Its ability to work long hours also improves its efficacy.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1453@LMC@2019-06-14
30005471@@@@@@Comparing to the existing methods, it is more reliable and cost-effective.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1454@LMC@2019-06-14
30005472@@@@@@Furthermore, little manpower is required to operate it and various situations can be tackled.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1455@LMC@2019-06-14
30005473@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1456@LMC@2019-06-14
30005474@@@@@@1@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1457@LMC@2019-06-14
30005475@@@@@@Pipe manufactures will supply the pipes.@@@@1@6@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1458@LMC@2019-06-14
30005476@@@@@@2@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1459@LMC@2019-06-14
30005477@@@@@@Mechanism to open /close the rain collection funnel and pipe ends will be designed and manufactured.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1460@LMC@2019-06-14
30005478@@@@@@3@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1461@LMC@2019-06-14
30005479@@@@@@Manufacturing of mouth will be outsourced to small companies.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1462@LMC@2019-06-14
30005480@@@@@@4@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1463@LMC@2019-06-14
30005481@@@@@@Local construction companies and contractors will integrate the system into buildings.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1464@LMC@2019-06-14
30005482@@@@@@Conclusion@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1465@LMC@2019-06-14
30005483@@@@@@The risk of excessive rainwater penetration in Singapore is increasing according to a study done by PUB.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1466@LMC@2019-06-14
30005484@@@@@@Flood Flusher aims to overcome the indoor flood problem more effectively and reliably to reduce the economic loss and disturbance to society.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:192; ntucle-sid:1467@LMC@2019-06-14
30005485@@@@@@NANYANG@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1419@LMC@2019-06-14
30005486@@@@@@TECHNOLOGICAL@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1420@LMC@2019-06-14
30005487@@@@@@UNIVERSITY@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1421@LMC@2019-06-14
30005488@@@@@@Proposal@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1422@LMC@2019-06-14
30005489@@@@@@Proposal Title: CIY Table@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1423@LMC@2019-06-14
30005490@@@@@@CIY (Clean-it-yourselves) Table@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1428@LMC@2019-06-14
30005491@@@@@@Background:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1429@LMC@2019-06-14
30005492@@@@@@In most of the schools and universities canteens, overcrowding has been one of the most common issues these years.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1430@LMC@2019-06-14
30005493@@@@@@(‘Our children are eating lunch on the canteen floor’, 2012) One of the causes of overcrowding is due to the unclean tables as diners choose to use the cleaned one.@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1431@LMC@2019-06-14
30005494@@@@@@Therefore, there are less useable tables when more and more tables are left unclean.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1432@LMC@2019-06-14
30005495@@@@@@Problem:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1433@LMC@2019-06-14
30005496@@@@@@Current method to clean the tables depends on the manpower.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1434@LMC@2019-06-14
30005497@@@@@@However, they have obvious limitations.@@@@1@5@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1435@LMC@2019-06-14
30005498@@@@@@During dining peak hours, they may find themselves becoming more and more exhausted and fail to cope up with the crowd’s demands.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1436@LMC@2019-06-14
30005499@@@@@@Besides, the tables might not be completely clean due to workers’ tiredness.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1437@LMC@2019-06-14
30005500@@@@@@To thoroughly eliminate this limitation, old method should be abandoned and technology should be brought into the management of canteen.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1438@LMC@2019-06-14
30005501@@@@@@Solution:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1439@LMC@2019-06-14
30005502@@@@@@In this article, CIY, an automated-cleaning table has been proposed.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1440@LMC@2019-06-14
30005503@@@@@@It has been developed with conveyor belt and automated-wiping mechanism.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1441@LMC@2019-06-14
30005504@@@@@@Once the diners finish their meal, by just a click on a button, the food residue will be removed in few seconds.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1442@LMC@2019-06-14
30005505@@@@@@The automated-whipping mechanism and water-spraying of CIY will make sure that the table will be kept hygienic for the next diners.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1443@LMC@2019-06-14
30005506@@@@@@In addition, the container in CIY is capable to store up to 200 diners’ food residue.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1444@LMC@2019-06-14
30005507@@@@@@Therefore, workers will only need to replace the container once per two days.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1445@LMC@2019-06-14
30005508@@@@@@The structure of table and automated whipping mechanism are as shown in diagram 1.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1446@LMC@2019-06-14
30005509@@@@@@Diagram 1@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1447@LMC@2019-06-14
30005510@@@@@@Benefit:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1448@LMC@2019-06-14
30005511@@@@@@CIY benefits massively crowded canteens and also the diners.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1449@LMC@2019-06-14
30005512@@@@@@Once the previous diner has finished his meal, by just a click, the table will then be ready to accommodate the next diners.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1450@LMC@2019-06-14
30005513@@@@@@The average time needed to have a table cleaned and ready for the next diners is minimized to less than 5 seconds.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1451@LMC@2019-06-14
30005514@@@@@@Looking at the greater picture, a canteen can efficiently accommodate more diners in a given time.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1452@LMC@2019-06-14
30005515@@@@@@Furthermore, the perfect hygienic condition provided by CIY will absolutely enhance the dining experience of all diners.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1453@LMC@2019-06-14
30005516@@@@@@As compared to the traditional method of cleaning, there is no such guarantee on the hygienic condition.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1454@LMC@2019-06-14
30005517@@@@@@Implementation:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1455@LMC@2019-06-14
30005518@@@@@@The implementation can be done in the following steps:@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1456@LMC@2019-06-14
30005519@@@@@@1@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1457@LMC@2019-06-14
30005520@@@@@@Collaboration with the hardware suppliers will be made to get the delivery of conveyor belt, rotating cylinder, whipping tool, container and custom made table.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1458@LMC@2019-06-14
30005521@@@@@@2@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1459@LMC@2019-06-14
30005522@@@@@@Collaboration with the software company to develop the application to automate cleaning process.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1460@LMC@2019-06-14
30005523@@@@@@3@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1461@LMC@2019-06-14
30005524@@@@@@The hardware parts will be assembled and tested with the developed software.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1462@LMC@2019-06-14
30005525@@@@@@Budget:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1463@LMC@2019-06-14
30005526@@@@@@Hardware cost (per table) $50@@@@1@5@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1464@LMC@2019-06-14
30005527@@@@@@Software development $200@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1465@LMC@2019-06-14
30005528@@@@@@Assembling and testing $20@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1466@LMC@2019-06-14
30005529@@@@@@Total $270@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1467@LMC@2019-06-14
30005530@@@@@@Conclusion:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1468@LMC@2019-06-14
30005531@@@@@@Overcrowded canteen has always been one of the most common problems recently, especially in schools and universities.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1469@LMC@2019-06-14
30005532@@@@@@Therefore, CIY aims to minimize the cleaning time and consequently leads to a better flow of diners in the canteen.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1470@LMC@2019-06-14
30005533@@@@@@In addition, CIY makes sure that the hygienic condition of tables to be up to mark.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1471@LMC@2019-06-14
30005534@@@@@@Addressing the overcrowding problem and hygienic concern, CIY promises to be an essential tool towards a better society.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:196; ntucle-sid:1472@LMC@2019-06-14
